*logtool-2.3.1-r2 (28 Mar 2014)

  28 Mar 2014; Mario Ackerl <mackerl@salomon.at> +logtool-2.3.1-r2.ebuild,
  +files/logtool-2.3.1-cycleTime.patch:
  Output in LogServer.log that cycleTime is greater than 500 ms increased to
  
  1500ms and is only written once every minute, bug#33949.

